{"tid":334063,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【荃灣劏場】地皇廣場劏舖68萬成交 勁蝕227萬","createTime":"2017-07-24T11:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:50:13.000Z","uid":17738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"19f20ddaa2e5d02ca4fd16cd9fc6c1af9141cafb","tid":334063,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170724/large/1500888471_53f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170724%2Flarge%2F1500888471_53f1.jpg&h=2eb34ed3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荃灣劏場地皇廣場再錄大幅蝕讓，商場3樓339號舖，建築面積82方呎，實用面積41方呎，以68萬元易手，呎價16,585元，與同區新盤海之戀相若。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2012年底一手購入，作價295萬元，持貨4年多，勁蝕227萬元，大幅貶值76.9%。是次成交價，與今年3月成交的3樓366號舖一樣，以68萬元沽出，同為商場入伙以來，舖價成交最低的舖位。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56996963&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56996963%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170724&d=QwmHDIQMkF5p0IdhLXjCGxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=44740d0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56996963%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170724&h=9a008df7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56996963&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170724</a>"},{"pid":"a6d6ed22028ae83e16846d02dea826870b353840","tid":334063,"uid":60787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0420b0348f7f8800160be190875b2b1de99da8d8","tid":334063,"uid":51041,"like":0,"disl